%% Data Science Pipelines Tekton - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Browser
    participant OAuthProxy as OAuth Proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant UI as ds-pipeline-ui<br/>3000/TCP HTTP
    participant API as ds-pipeline API<br/>8888/TCP HTTP
    participant MySQL as MySQL/MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Tekton as Tekton PipelineRun
    participant PA as Persistence Agent
    participant SW as ScheduledWorkflow<br/>Controller
    participant MinIO as S3/MinIO<br/>9000/TCP
    participant MW as metadata-writer
    participant Envoy as metadata-envoy<br/>9090/TCP gRPC
    participant MLMD as metadata-grpc<br/>8080/TCP gRPC

    Note over User, Tekton: Flow 1: Pipeline Execution
    User->>OAuthProxy: HTTPS/8443<br/>OAuth Token
    OAuthProxy->>UI: HTTP/3000<br/>plaintext (local)
    UI->>API: HTTP/8888<br/>REST API call
    API->>MySQL: MySQL/3306<br/>Username/Password
    API->>K8sAPI: HTTPS/443<br/>ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI->>Tekton: Create PipelineRun

    Note over PA, API: Flow 2: Pipeline Status Sync
    PA->>K8sAPI: HTTPS/443 Watch PipelineRuns<br/>ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>PA: PipelineRun status updates
    PA->>API: HTTP/8888<br/>Sync status (plaintext)

    Note over Tekton, MLMD: Flow 3: Artifact Tracking
    Tekton->>MinIO: HTTP/9000<br/>AccessKey/SecretKey<br/>Artifact upload
    MW->>K8sAPI: HTTPS/443 Watch PipelineRuns<br/>ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>MW: PipelineRun events
    MW->>Envoy: gRPC/9090<br/>plaintext
    Envoy->>MLMD: gRPC/8080<br/>plaintext
    MLMD->>MySQL: MySQL/3306<br/>Username/Password

    Note over SW, Tekton: Flow 4: Scheduled Pipeline Run
    SW->>K8sAPI: HTTPS/443 Watch ScheduledWorkflows<br/>ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>SW: ScheduledWorkflow events
    SW->>K8sAPI: HTTPS/443 Create PipelineRun<br/>ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI->>Tekton: Create PipelineRun (on cron schedule)
